{"captions":[{"content":"我喜歡樹，而我很幸運，","startTime":0,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"因為我們住在一個很棒的植物園附近，","startTime":3000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"通常在星期天的時候，我會和我太太到那裡走走，","startTime":6000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"現在則是和我四歲的小孩去那裡，","startTime":9000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們會爬上樹梢，或是在樹林裡玩躲迷藏。","startTime":11000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我讀的第二所學校也有很雄偉的樹，","startTime":14000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有一株很美的鵝掌楸，我想大概是全國最大的吧...","startTime":18000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"還有很棒的灌木叢和一些花草樹木，","startTime":22000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"就在遊戲區附近。","startTime":26000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有一天，我被幾個同學捉住，","startTime":28000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"他們把我帶進灌木叢裡，扒掉我的衣服打我，","startTime":32000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我被毒打一頓，後來還造成了憂鬱症。","startTime":36000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我現在說出來的原因是，我認為，經過了這些事--","startTime":41000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"嗯，後來我回到學校，我覺得自己很骯髒、被人背叛了，","startTime":45000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我也覺得很羞恥，但是主要還是無力感。","startTime":51000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"三十年之後，我在搭乘一架飛機的時候，","startTime":58000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"隔壁坐了一位來自智利的女士，她叫做薇若妮卡，","startTime":61000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們一同參與某個人權團體行程，","startTime":64000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"她告訴我被人虐待的感覺是什麼，","startTime":67000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而我剛好有那個獨特的經驗，","startTime":72000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"於是我便和她分享我那唯一的經驗。","startTime":75000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那真是一次很棒的學習經驗，","startTime":79000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"因為對我來說，人權只不過是我個人","startTime":81000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"休閒時的興趣，但是對其他人來說，","startTime":84000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"卻是真實的發生在自己身上的事。","startTime":87000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我在1985年時接到波諾(Bono)的電話，","startTime":90000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"大家都知道他是很棒的歌手，但我覺得他嘴上功夫也很好--","startTime":97000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"(笑聲)","startTime":102000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"你很難拒絕這個人，他總有他的說法。","startTime":104000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"就在我完成Biko(南非人權運動者)的紀念專輯後，","startTime":107000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們正要為國際特赦組織進行巡迴演出，","startTime":109000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他說：你真的得加入我們。那是我第一次","startTime":111000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"站出來認識這麼多朋友，","startTime":114000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們有的人親眼看到自己的親人被槍殺，","startTime":118000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有的親人被人從飛機上丟下大海，","startTime":121000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"突然之間，我的世界裡多了人權議題，","startTime":124000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我再也無法像以前那樣不聞不問了。","startTime":129000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"所以我就加入了那次巡迴演出，那是為國際特赦組織所做的演出，","startTime":134000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"然後在1988年，我接替波諾的工作開始騙人，","startTime":138000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我做得沒有那麼好，但我設法讓尤蘇．安多爾、史汀、","startTime":143000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"崔西．查普曼和布魯斯．史普林斯汀一起加入這場巡演，","startTime":147000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那真是一個很棒的經驗。","startTime":152000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而且，我從中學到了很特別的東西，","startTime":155000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那是我第一次","startTime":159000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"認識這麼多來自不同國家的人，","startTime":161000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們的人權故事是那麼具體，","startTime":165000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我一樣沒辦法假裝不聞不問。","startTime":170000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但真正令我驚訝而我也搞不懂的是，","startTime":176000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"人們在受到這麼具大的創傷後，","startTime":179000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"加害者竟會全盤否認那些經歷、那些故事，","startTime":182000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"只為掩蓋和遺忘這些罪行。","startTime":188000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但只要那附近有照相機、","startTime":191000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"錄影機或攝影機，","startTime":196000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"當權者要掩蓋他們的罪行就沒有那麼容易了。","startTime":199000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"銳跑(Reebok)公司在我們的人權巡演之後，設立了一個基金會，","startTime":206000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們決定要--","startTime":210000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"嗯，我們在幾年前提出了一個建議，","startTime":214000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們希望在基金會裡設立一個部門，","startTime":217000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"由這個部門發放攝影機給人權運動領袖。","startTime":219000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"這個建議在當時並沒有被採納，","startTime":224000,"duration":1000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"然而，在1992年洛杉磯暴動發生後，人們開始思考，","startTime":225000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"若我們能在對的時間、對的地點放上一台攝影機，","startTime":228000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"或許就算是在錯誤的時間，要看你是什麼人，","startTime":231000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你或許就能發揮某些作用，","startTime":235000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"發起某項運動，為自己發聲，","startTime":240000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"告訴世人發生了什麼事。","startTime":244000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"證人計畫在1992年開始運作，","startTime":246000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"發放攝影機到超過60個國家，","startTime":250000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們和其他團體一起發起運動，","startTime":256000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"幫助他們訴說他們的故事，","startTime":262000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"等一下我會告訴你們，最近的一個運動，","startTime":266000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那是在烏干達發生的故事，","startTime":270000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"雖然我們昨天有聽到關於烏干達美好的故事，","startTime":273000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但這一個不是美好的故事。","startTime":277000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"在烏干達北部，","startTime":279000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"大約有一百五十萬流離失所的烏干達人民，","startTime":281000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們不是來自其他國家的難民，","startTime":284000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而是長達20年來烏干達內戰的難民，","startTime":287000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們沒有地方去。","startTime":291000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"有二萬個孩童被徵召成為兒童兵，","startTime":293000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"國際刑事法庭目前在追捕五個軍事領導人，","startTime":299000,"duration":8000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們叫什麼名字呢？","startTime":307000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我忘了軍隊的名稱，","startTime":309000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"大概是叫做聖主反抗軍吧...","startTime":311000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但是烏干達政府也好不到哪裡去，","startTime":314000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"讓我們先來看第一支影片。","startTime":316000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"(音樂)","startTime":318000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"女性：生活在難民營裡不容易，即使到今天也是一樣，","startTime":321000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們擔心迫使我們逃到難民營的恐怖事件，","startTime":324000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"到今天還在家鄉持續上演。","startTime":328000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"文字：「進退二難：受虐，或逃到烏干達北部」","startTime":334000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"男性：我們在家鄉的時候，科尼的反叛軍一直在騷擾我們，","startTime":345000,"duration":7000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"一開始來到難民營時還滿安全的，","startTime":352000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但之後，政府軍就開始虐待我們。","startTime":355000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"(軍歌聲)","startTime":360000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"珍妮佛：一個軍人走在路上，問我們從哪裡來，","startTime":363000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"艾佛琳和我躲在媽媽後面。","startTime":367000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"艾佛琳：他命令我們坐下，所以我們就坐下來，","startTime":373000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"又來了另一個軍人。","startTime":376000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"珍妮佛：那個人過來把我的衣服脫掉，","startTime":379000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"另一個就把艾佛琳帶走，","startTime":383000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"猥褺我的那個人後來跑去強暴艾佛琳，","startTime":386000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"之前強暴艾佛琳的人則又跑來猥褺我。♫","startTime":391000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"男性：拿著長長棍子的軍人毒打我們，要我們招認，","startTime":395000,"duration":8000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們一邊毒打我們，一邊說：「快招認！」","startTime":403000,"duration":12000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"女性：他們一直認為我在說謊，","startTime":415000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"所以就開槍射斷了我的手指，","startTime":420000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我倒了下來，他們跑回原隊伍，就讓我在那裡等死。","startTime":425000,"duration":9000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"(音樂)","startTime":438000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"文字：烏干達在1986年通過了反虐待公約。","startTime":440000,"duration":9000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"凡憑藉公權力，意圖獲取資訊、","startTime":449000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"逼供、處罰、","startTime":453000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"脅迫或恫嚇，而刻意將巨大的痛楚","startTime":456000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"施加於另一人的身體或心理，都被定義為虐待。","startTime":460000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"不是只有別的國家才會有虐待的事情發生，","startTime":468000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"在我們國家，","startTime":474000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"就有英國軍人毒打年輕伊拉克人的照片曝光，","startTime":476000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"還有阿布格來布監獄和關達那摩監獄(均有虐囚案)，","startTime":483000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"載我到紐渥克機場的司機，","startTime":485000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他告訴我，某天半夜四點鐘，","startTime":488000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他被人從皇后區的家中帶走，帶到（美國）中西部，","startTime":494000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"在那裡被人毒打和審問，","startTime":500000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"四個星期之後才被放走，","startTime":504000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"只因為他是中東人，而他的名字，","startTime":508000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他的名字剛好和911事件中的飛機駕駛同名。","startTime":511000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"這件事或許是真的，也有可能是假的，","startTime":515000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但我認為他沒有說謊。","startTime":519000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我想，在我們觀看這個世界的同時，","startTime":522000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"北極冰山正在溶化，","startTime":526000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而我們奮鬥了","startTime":528000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"幾個世紀的人權，","startTime":531000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"也正快速地被侵蝕，","startTime":534000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"或許，人權是值得我們觀注的議題，","startTime":537000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"我們或許也該為人權做些事了。","startTime":541000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"就在這裡，我們有一位夥伴，參加了范瓊斯所發起的","startTime":545000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"「要教育，不要監獄」活動，","startTime":550000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們希望能在加州用影片","startTime":554000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"來改變目前的青少年行為矯正體系，","startTime":557000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"他們在找的是更有人性的作法，","startTime":562000,"duration":5000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"而不只是把青少年關在監獄，","startTime":567000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那絕對是個不好的開始。","startTime":571000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"就像道德先生這個故事所講的，","startTime":573000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"「抱歉，凱柏爾先生，","startTime":579000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你介意我們將你的死刑延後一點嗎？」","startTime":581000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"「不會，沒問題，就慢慢來吧。」","startTime":585000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但不管那個人是誰、做了什麼，","startTime":588000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"那都是殘忍且特殊的處罰。","startTime":594000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"證人計畫要做的是去武裝那些勇敢的人，","startTime":598000,"duration":6000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"他們冒著生命危險，帶著攝影機到世界各地，","startTime":604000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"讓我們再看一段影片，謝謝。","startTime":608000,"duration":3000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"(雷聲)","startTime":616000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"(音樂)","startTime":619000,"duration":4000,"startOfParagraph":true},{"content":"文字：你可以說陪審團貪污，","startTime":623000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你也可以指控某人說謊，","startTime":628000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"你也可以說你不相信報紙，","startTime":635000,"duration":2000,"startOfParagraph":false},{"content":"但你不能說","startTi